<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Privacy Policy — BotStop</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="${docroot}/static/img/botstop-icon.svg">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #0a0a0a; color: #e2e8f0; line-height: 1.7; }
    .nav { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(5,156,215,0.2); padding: 0 40px; height: 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .nav a { color: #059CD7; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .content { max-width: 760px; margin: 80px auto 60px; padding: 0 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .updated { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #059CD7; margin: 32px 0 12px; }
    p, li { color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    a { color: #059CD7; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="${docroot}/">BotStop</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: July 2, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. What We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use BotStop, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your email address and name (via Google Sign-In or email/password registration)</li>
      <li>Scan targets you submit (domain names, IP addresses, etc.)</li>
      <li>Scan results and findings generated by our OSINT engine</li>
      <li>Basic usage logs (scan timestamps, status)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use It</h2>
    <p>We use this data solely to provide the BotStop service — running security scans on your behalf and displaying results to you. We do not sell your data, share it with third parties for advertising, or use it for any purpose other than operating the service.</p>

    <h2>3. Scan Data</h2>
    <p>Scan targets and results are stored in our database to allow you to review historical scans. You can delete any scan from the Scans page at any time. Deleted scans are permanently removed.</p>

    <h2>4. Google Sign-In</h2>
    <p>If you sign in with Google, we receive your name, email address, and profile picture from Google. We do not receive your Google password or access to any Google services beyond basic profile information.</p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>All data is transmitted over HTTPS. Your scan data is stored on servers we control and is not accessible to other users.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:support@botstopaudit.com">support@botstopaudit.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
